node.text: She’s my mini but…. I’m not sure who the “mini” is… 😂😃 I look so short next to my baby @nataliabryant and she’s 5’10”! (I’m 5’5”)🙃🤓

Natalia’s MET Gala dress arriving in the Archive Box.  American Lexicon Exhibit Dress.  American themed Met Gala~ 60’s vibes. Designed by @connerives ❤️(Thankfully it gets a new box after the red carpet 😃)DETAILS ➡️➡️➡️➡️
